(484, 3, '2017-05-17 16:57:12', '2017-05-17 11:27:12', '<span style="font-weight: 400;">No bill in this regard has been tabled in Parliament since BJP government has come to power. However, the ministry </span><a href="http://www.moef.nic.in/sites/default/files/ScanJobInvitation%20of%20comments%20Draft%20Environment%20Law.pdf"><span style="font-weight: 400;">drafted</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;"> a bill in this regard and uploaded on its website in October 2015 but no progress has been made since then. </span>', 'Frame the environment laws in a manner that provides no scope for confusion and will lead to speedy clearance of proposals without delay', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'frame-the-environment-laws-in-a-manner-that-provides-no-scope-for-confusion-and-will-lead-to-speedy-clearance-of-proposals-without-delay', '', '', '2017-05-27 18:07:49', '2017-05-27 12:37:49', '', 0, 'http://www.electionpromisestracker.in/?post_type=promise&#038;p=484', 0, 'promise', '', 0),
(485, 3, '2017-05-17 16:53:49', '2017-05-17 11:23:49', '<span style="font-weight: 400;">Fiscal deficit as a percentage of GDP has been </span><a href="http://www.tradingeconomics.com/india/government-budget"><span style="font-weight: 400;">reduced</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;"> from 4.5 % in 2014 to 3.5 % in 2016, </span><a href="http://www.tradingeconomics.com/india/government-budget"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Trading Economics</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;"> reported. This has been maintained without compromising on  fund availability as </span><a href="http://indiabudget.nic.in/ub2017-18/bag/bag6.pdf"><span style="font-weight: 400;">total expenditure</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;"> has been increased from 18 Lakh crores in Financial Year 2015-16 to 20 Lakh crores in Financial Year 2016-17.</span>\r\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">Net borrowings per rupee spent have been</span><a href="http://www.livemint.com/Politics/TjGjdavgyZ5U3OJs6XrLzO/Arun-Jaitleys-path-to-fiscal-discipline.html"> <span style="font-weight: 400;">reduced</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;"> from 28 paise in 2014 to 17 paisa in 2017. </span>', 'Strictly implement Fiscal discipline, without compromising on funds availability for development work and asset creation', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'strictly-implement-fiscal-discipline-without-compromising-on-funds-availability-for-development-work-and-asset-creation', '', '', '2017-05-19 15:08:29', '2017-05-19 09:38:29', '', 0, 'http://www.electionpromisestracker.in/?post_type=promise&#038;p=485', 0, 'promise', '', 0),
(486, 3, '2017-05-17 16:58:07', '2017-05-17 11:28:07', 'The BJP government launched <a href="http://pib.nic.in/newsite/PrintRelease.aspx?relid=155999">“Uchchtar Avishkaar Yojana”</a> in 2016 to promote industry-academia relationships. The project is currently been piloted in IITs. 92 projects have been approved till Jan 2017. A <a href="http://mhrd.gov.in/sites/upload_files/mhrd/files/ru2388.pdf">Council for Industry &amp; Higher Education Collaboration (CIHEC)</a> was also constituted with representatives from both academia and industry.\r\nThe <a href="http://www.aicte-india.org/downloads/Startup%20Policy.pdf">Start-Up Policy</a> formulated by the All India Council for Technical Education promotes student driven start ups by various measure including industry-academia interaction.', 'Institute a mechanism for interaction between industry (including SME), academia & community', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'institute-a-mechanism-for-interaction-between-industry-including-sme-academia-community', '', '', '2017-05-19 13:37:44', '2017-05-19 08:07:44', '', 0, 'http://www.electionpromisestracker.in/?post_type=promise&#038;p=486', 0, 'promise', '', 0),
