(512, 3, '2017-05-17 17:04:14', '2017-05-17 11:34:14', '<span style="font-weight: 400;">BJP government set up Custom Clearance </span><a href="http://www.business-standard.com/article/pti-stories/govt-sets-up-ccfcs-at-ports-to-expedite-customs-clearance-115070700626_1.html"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Facilitation Centres</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;"> (CCFCs) at major Indian seaports &amp; Airports in July 2015 to ensure easier clearances. A </span><a href="http://www.cbec.gov.in/htdocs-cbec/customs/cs-circulars/cs-circulars-2015/circ-13-2015cs"><span style="font-weight: 400;">committee</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;"> was formed with immediate effect from April 2015. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">CBEC (Central Board of Excise &amp; Customs) launched Single window interface for facilitating Trade (</span><a href="http://www.thehindubusinessline.com/economy/indian-customs-launches-swift-clearances/article8426720.ece"><span style="font-weight: 400;">SWIFT</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;">) in April 2016 for quick single window custom clearances  for import. The </span><a href="https://www.icegate.gov.in/SWIFT/index.html"><span style="font-weight: 400;">portal</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;"> has been operational under CBEC website.</span>\r\n\r\nSince there has been an improvement in custom clearances after setting up felicitation centers, the progress has been classified as adequate.', 'Set up trade facilitation to ensure easier customs clearances', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'set-up-trade-facilitation-to-ensure-easier-customs-clearances', '', '', '2017-05-27 23:45:07', '2017-05-27 18:15:07', '', 0, 'http://www.electionpromisestracker.in/?post_type=promise&#038;p=512', 0, 'promise', '', 0),
