(520, 3, '2017-05-17 17:08:31', '2017-05-17 11:38:31', '<span style="font-weight: 400;">No dedicated bank has been set up for ensuring availability of credit for SMEs but the government has set up</span><a href="http://www.nsicffconline.in/"> <span style="font-weight: 400;">Finance Facilitation Centre</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;"> (an online portal) which allows MSMEs to apply for loans from various banks on NSIC Portal.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">BJP government has boosted up the</span><a href="https://www.cgtmse.in/"> <span style="font-weight: 400;">Credit Guarantee Scheme</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;"> set up in 2000, covering more than 5 lakhs guarantee approvals in the year 2015-16, which is the highest so far. It has registered a growth of about 28% over the previous Financial year.</span>\r\n\r\nThough no dedicated bank has been established, the government has taken significant measures to avail credit. Hence, this promise has been classified as adequate.', 'Ensure availability of credit through a dedicated SME bank', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'ensure-availability-of-credit-through-a-dedicated-sme-bank', '', '', '2017-05-27 23:57:32', '2017-05-27 18:27:32', '', 0, 'http://www.electionpromisestracker.in/?post_type=promise&#038;p=520', 0, 'promise', '', 0),
