(541, 3, '2017-05-17 17:18:15', '2017-05-17 11:48:15', '<span style="font-weight: 400;">In January, 2016, BJP government</span><a href="http://startupindia.gov.in/status.php"><span style="font-weight: 400;"> launched Start-Up India Action Plan</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;"> to empower start-ups to grow and innovate. 932 Start-up applications have been approved so far.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">BJP government has </span><a href="http://www.financialexpress.com/budget/union-budget-2017-good-news-for-small-companies-now-pay-only-25-tax/532458/"><span style="font-weight: 400;">reduced the income tax</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;"> for the companies with an annual turnover of less than 50 lakhs to 25% from April,2017 in Budget 2017-18.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">BJP government is initiating a </span><a href="http://economictimes.indiatimes.com/small-biz/startups/governments-credit-guarantee-scheme-to-give-startups-a-loan-lifeline-of-up-to-rs-5-crore/articleshow/57610609.cms"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Credit Guarantee scheme</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;"> to give start-ups a loan life of up to Rs. 5 Crore., awaiting Cabinet approval.</span>', 'Encourage and empower our youth for self-employment - incubating entrepreneurship as well as facilitating credit', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'encourage-and-empower-our-youth-for-self-employment-incubating-entrepreneurship-as-well-as-facilitating-credit', '', '', '2017-05-28 00:41:04', '2017-05-27 19:11:04', '', 0, 'http://www.electionpromisestracker.in/?post_type=promise&#038;p=541', 0, 'promise', '', 0),
(542, 3, '2017-05-17 17:18:42', '2017-05-17 11:48:42', 'No such commission has been set up by the BJP government. A <a href="http://mhrd.gov.in/sites/upload_files/mhrd/files/nep/press-releases.pdf">Drafting Committee</a> was set up to prepare a <a href="http://nuepa.org/NEW/download/NEP2016/ReportNEP.pdf">draft NEP</a>, however, the policy hasn’t been accepted by the BJP government. <a href="http://www.livemint.com/Education/D1P0mMtV13lMa86gJjbA9H/Govt-to-announce-new-panel-for-drafting-National-Education-P.html">No new committee</a> has been set up by the government to prepare a new draft for NEP.\r\n\r\nSince the new committee is yet to be set up, the performance against this promise has been classified as "Yet to Start"', 'Set up a National Commission on Education to recommend New Education Policy (NEP)', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'set-up-a-national-commission-on-education-to-recommend-new-education-policy-nep', '', '', '2017-05-19 01:08:43', '2017-05-18 19:38:43', '', 0, 'http://www.electionpromisestracker.in/?post_type=promise&#038;p=542', 0, 'promise', '', 0),
