(544, 3, '2017-05-17 17:19:28', '2017-05-17 11:49:28', '<span style="font-weight: 400;">BJP government </span><a href="http://www.financialexpress.com/economy/employment-opportunities-to-1-crore-youth-by-2020-bandaru-dattatreya/517086/"><span style="font-weight: 400;">decided</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;"> to transform 100 Employment Exchanges out of 978 existing centres into </span><a href="http://www.mcc-centre.com/"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Model Career Centres</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;"> (MCC). </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">The Government </span><a href="http://www.business-standard.com/article/government-press-release/upgradation-of-employment-exchanges-117020800698_1.html"><span style="font-weight: 400;">provides financial assistance</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;"> to these centres upto Rs 50 lakh per centre based on the proposals and scheme guidelines. The Centre has already </span><a href="http://www.business-standard.com/article/economy-policy/coming-soon-model-career-centres-for-jobseekers-116012600013_1.html"><span style="font-weight: 400;">allocated money</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;"> to states for 70 such centres. The portal provides the data only for three such centres at Gurgaon, Mumbai and Chennai.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">Ministry of Labour &amp; Employment launched National Career Center (NCS) </span><a href="https://www.ncs.gov.in/Pages/default.aspx"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Portal</span></a> <span style="font-weight: 400;">to transform the existing National Employment Service &amp; </span><a href="http://pib.nic.in/newsite/printrelease.aspx?relid=161407"><span style="font-weight: 400;">linking all employment exchanges</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;"> of the country. The Centre partly funded the IT upgradation for this initiative.</span>\r\n\r\nSince information for only three such centres has been given &amp; the progress is very slow, the progress has been classified as inadequate.', 'Transform our Employment Exchanges into Career Centres - connecting our youth with job opportunities as well as providing counselling and training', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'transform-our-employment-exchanges-into-career-centres-connecting-our-youth-with-job-opportunities-in-a-transparent-and-effective-manner-through-the-use-of-technology-as-well-as-providing-counselli', '', '', '2017-05-28 00:45:00', '2017-05-27 19:15:00', '', 0, 'http://www.electionpromisestracker.in/?post_type=promise&#038;p=544', 0, 'promise', '', 0),
