(546, 3, '2017-05-17 17:20:33', '2017-05-17 11:50:33', 'No new scheme has been started by the BJP government in the past 3 years. However, the government continues with the <a href="http://tribal.nic.in/Content/Access%20Schemes.aspx">previously run schemes</a> which establish schools, hostels, and vocational training centers. Under these schemes, the number of schools has increased from <a href="http://164.100.47.134/lsscommittee/Social%20Justice%20&amp;%20Empowerment/15_Social_Justice_And_Empowerment_44.pdf">862 in the year 2014</a> to <a href="http://164.100.47.194/Loksabha/Questions/QResult15.aspx?qref=46725&amp;lsno=16">1,205 in the year 2017</a>. The <a href="https://www.unicef.org/infobycountry/stats_popup5.html">Gross Enrollment Ratio (GER)</a> at primary level for STs decreased from <a href="http://164.100.47.190/loksabhaquestions/annex/10/AU3114.pdf">105.5% in 2013-14 to 103.3% in 2015-16</a>. The GER at secondary level for STs increased from <a href="http://164.100.47.190/loksabhaquestions/annex/10/AU3114.pdf">70.2% in 2013-14 to 74.53% in 2015-16</a>.', 'Set up the entire education network for tribal', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'set-up-the-entire-education-network-for-tribal', '', '', '2017-05-19 15:01:46', '2017-05-19 09:31:46', '', 0, 'http://www.electionpromisestracker.in/?post_type=promise&#038;p=546', 0, 'promise', '', 0),
