(654, 3, '2017-05-18 12:00:23', '2017-05-18 06:30:23', '<a href="http://pib.nic.in/newsite/PrintRelease.aspx?relid=156054">Atal Pension Yojna</a>(APY), launched in 2015, provides for pension ranging from <a href="http://pib.nic.in/newsite/PrintRelease.aspx?relid=156054">Rs.1000 to Rs. 5000</a> for people from unorganized sector and for farmers above the age of 60 years. Maximum age for registering under the Yojna is 40 years and the pension is paid after the person reaches 60 years of age. A total of <a href="http://pib.nic.in/newsite/PrintRelease.aspx?relid=156054">38 lakh</a> subscribers have been enrolled under APY with a total pension wealth of <a href="http://pib.nic.in/newsite/PrintRelease.aspx?relid=156054">Rs. 1350 crore</a> per month.\r\n\r\n<a href="http://pib.nic.in/newsite/PrintRelease.aspx?relid=136995">Krishi kalyan cess</a>, a 0.5% cess on all taxable services, is designed to finance initiatives relating to improvement of agriculture and welfare of farmers. This was launched by the BJP government in February 2016.\r\n\r\nHowever, farmers suicide continue to rise from <a href="http://www.business-standard.com/article/economy-policy/farmer-suicides-went-up-to-12-360-in-2014-report-115071800758_1.html">11,772 </a>in 2013 to <a href="http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/farmer-suicides-up-42-between-2014-2015/articleshow/56363591.cms">12,602</a> in 2015.', 'Put in place welfare measures for farmers above 60 years of age, small and marginal farmers and farm labours', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '564-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-05-18 12:00:23', '2017-05-18 06:30:23', '', 564, 'http://www.electionpromisestracker.in/564-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(655, 3, '2017-05-18 12:07:19', '2017-05-18 06:37:19', 'BJP government has approved a new scheme <a href="http://pib.nic.in/newsite/PrintRelease.aspx?relid=161512">SAMPADA</a> for the development of infrastructure for agro-processing clusters. The scheme has a budget overlay of Rs. 6000 crores for the period 2016-20. The agro-food processing clusters are intended to create cluster based storage systems for perishable goods like vegetables and fruits.\r\n\r\nHowever, No clusters have been set up till date.', 'Create Cluster based storage systems (e.g. Rice cluster, Wheat Cluster, Veg - Fruit cluster, Spices cluster)', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'create-cluster-based-storage-systems-e-g-rice-cluster-wheat-cluster-veg-fruit-cluster-spices-cluster', '', '', '2017-05-19 11:31:33', '2017-05-19 06:01:33', '', 0, 'http://www.electionpromisestracker.in/?post_type=promise&#038;p=655', 0, 'promise', '', 0),
