(711, 7, '2017-05-18 13:38:28', '2017-05-18 08:08:28', '<a href="https://thewire.in/106575/health-budget-2017-18/">Budgetary allocation to National Rural Health M<u>ission (NRHM)</u></a>, as total percentage of total health budget has fallen from 52.6% in 2015-16 to 43.4% in 2017-18. Under NRHM, the share of ‘Infrastructure maintenance’ has constantly fallen from <a href="https://thewire.in/106575/health-budget-2017-18/">28.5% in 2015-16 to 26% in 2017-18.</a> Low budgetary allocation will impede the progress of modernisation and upgradation of health infrastructure.\r\n\r\nGovernment launched many apps like <a href="http://pib.nic.in/newsite/PrintRelease.aspx?relid=155854">Swachh Bharat app, ANM Online Application(ANMOL), Kilkari</a>, etc and initiated other digital platforms like <a href="https://www.nhp.gov.in/">National Health Portal</a>, <a href="http://ors.gov.in/index.html">Online Registration System</a>, to bring latest technologies in healthcare sector.', 'Modernize Government hospitals, upgrading infrastructure and latest technologies', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '623-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-05-18 13:38:28', '2017-05-18 08:08:28', '', 623, 'http://www.electionpromisestracker.in/623-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(712, 3, '2017-05-18 13:56:02', '2017-05-18 08:26:02', 'No government order or legislation has been issued that makes it mandatory for the government to digitise government work. Therefore, the promise has been classified as "Yet to Start".', 'Mandate digitization of all government work to reduce corruption and delays', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'mandate-digitization-of-all-government-work-to-reduce-corruption-and-delays', '', '', '2017-05-18 23:10:07', '2017-05-18 17:40:07', '', 0, 'http://www.electionpromisestracker.in/?post_type=promise&#038;p=712', 0, 'promise', '', 0),
