agriculture, transparency, law and order, minority rights, culture, and many more.\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_blurb][et_pb_blurb admin_label="Blurb" title="Fact-Check Claims" url_new_window="off" use_icon="on" font_icon="%%49%%" icon_color="#ffffff" use_circle="on" use_circle_border="off" circle_border_color="#2ea3f2" icon_placement="left" animation="top" background_layout="light" text_orientation="center" url="Fact checking any statement or claim issued by our elected representatives. No opinion, Only 100% verified Facts" circle_color="#2ea3f2" use_icon_font_size="off" use_border_color="off" border_color="#ffffff" border_style="solid"]\r\n\r\nFact checking any statement or claim issued by our elected representatives. No opinion, Only 100% verified Facts\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_blurb][et_pb_blurb admin_label="Blurb" title="Discuss &amp; Spread" url_new_window="off" use_icon="on" font_icon="%%222%%" icon_color="#ffffff" use_circle="on" use_circle_border="off" circle_border_color="#2ea3f2" icon_placement="left" animation="top" background_layout="light" text_orientation="center" circle_color="#2ea3f2" use_icon_font_size="off" use_border_color="off" border_color="#ffffff" border_style="solid"]\r\n\r\nEnable community dialogue, and help spread right information to the world.\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_blurb][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section bb_built="1" admin_label="section" fullwidth="off" specialty="off" inner_shadow="off" parallax="off"][et_pb_row admin_label="row"][et_pb_column type="4_4"][et_pb_divider admin_label="Divider" color="#27323a" show_divider="on" height="30" divider_style="solid" divider_position="top" hide_on_mobile="on"] [/et_pb_divider][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row admin_label="Row"][et_pb_column type="4_4"][et_pb_text admin_label="Text" background_layout="light" text_orientation="center" use_border_color="off" border_color="#ffffff" border_style="solid"]\r\n<h1>Our Vision!</h1>\r\nTo track every government on every sector by 2020. This is a work in progress and we require your help in tracking the performance of the rest of the state and localgovernments. If you share our love for democracy, please write to us atjoinus@electionpromisestracker.in and will figure out ways of collaboration.\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section bb_built="1" admin_label="section" fullwidth="off" specialty="off" inner_shadow="on" parallax="off" transparent_background="off" allow_player_pause="off" parallax_method="off" make_fullwidth="off" use_custom_width="off" width_unit="on" make_equal="off" use_custom_gutter="off"][et_pb_row admin_label="row"][et_pb_column type="4_4"][et_pb_cta admin_label="Call To Action" button_url="#" button_text="Register" use_background_color="on" background_color="#ffffff" background_layout="light" text_orientation="center" title="Subscribe to Our Updates!" url_new_window="off" use_border_color="off" border_color="#ffffff" border_style="solid" custom_button="off" button_letter_spacing="0" button_use_icon="default" button_icon_placement="right" button_on_hover="on" button_letter_spacing_hover="0"]\r\n\r\nRegister here to receive email notifications about our latest updates!\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_cta][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section]', 'Home', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '36-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-05-18 16:21:52', '2017-05-18 10:51:52', '', 36, 'http://www.electionpromisestracker.in/36-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(800, 3, '2017-05-21 03:52:44', '2017-05-20 22:22:44', '<p>[et_pb_section bb_built="1" admin_label="section" background_color="#00a06b" inner_shadow="on" fullwidth="on" transparent_background="off" allow_player_pause="off" parallax="off" parallax_method="off" make_fullwidth="off" use_custom_width="off" width_unit="on" make_equal="off" use_custom_gutter="off"][et_pb_fullwidth_header admin_label="Fullwidth Header" title="Our Team" text_orientation="justified" background_layout="dark" header_fullscreen="off" header_scroll_down="off" parallax="off" parallax_method="off" content_orientation="center" image_orientation="center" custom_button_one="off" button_one_letter_spacing="0" button_one_use_icon="default" button_one_icon_placement="right" button_one_on_hover="on" button_one_letter_spacing_hover="0" custom_button_two="off" button_two_letter_spacing="0" button_two_use_icon="default" button_two_icon_placement="right" button_two_on_hover="on" button_two_letter_spacing_hover="0"]</p><p>Election Promises Tracker is an initiative of a group of citizens connected by their love for democracy.</p><p>[/et_pb_fullwidth_header][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section bb_built="1" admin_label="section" fullwidth="off" specialty="off"][et_pb_row admin_label="row"][et_pb_column type="1_3"][et_pb_team_member admin_label="Team Member" name="Anurag Kundu" position="Co-Founder" image_url="http://www.electionpromisestracker.in/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/pp-1-190x190.jpg" animation="fade_in" background_layout="light" facebook_url="https://www.facebook.com/anurag.kundu" twitter_url="https://twitter.com/anuragkunduak?lang=en" use_border_color="off" border_color="#ffffff" border_style="solid" custom_css_member_image="{|| height: 250px !important; width:250px;||}"]</p><p><strong>Anurag </strong>works with Ministry of Education, Government of Delhi. He was preciously involved in the drafting of Education Manifesto of Aam Aadmi Party for Delhi Elections 2015.</p><p>[/et_pb_team_member][et_pb_text admin_label="Text" /][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type="1_3"][et_pb_team_member admin_label="Team Member" name="Anup Kalbalia" position="Co-Founder" image_url="http://www.electionpromisestracker.in/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/16473714_1617510591609009_9073309239860008602_n-250x182.jpg" animation="fade_in" background_layout="light" facebook_url="https://www.facebook.com/search/top/?q=anup%20kalbalia" twitter_url="https://twitter.com/anupkal?lang=en" use_border_color="off" border_color="#ffffff" border_style="solid" custom_css_member_image=" { height: 100px;|| width: 100px; }"]</p><p><strong>Anup </strong>works with Directi, a software products company. In his free time he likes to meet people over a cup of coffee, a mug of beer or a few glasses of fresh fruit juices to discuss politics.</p><p>[/et_pb_team_member][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type="1_3"][et_pb_team_member admin_label="Team Member" name="Rashmi Singh" position="Lead Researcher" image_url="http://www.electionpromisestracker.in/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/10014530_983031268392169_5083362588198484624_n-250x185-1.jpg" animation="fade_in" background_layout="light" facebook_url="https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=1303472202" use_border_color="off" border_color="#ffffff" border_style="solid"]</p><p><strong>Rashmi Singh</strong> is passionate about politics and yearns to strengthen democracy. A student of economics and a Teach For India fellow, she seeks to lead a meaningful life.</p><p>[/et_pb_team_member][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row admin_label="row"][et_pb_column type="1_3"][et_pb_team_member admin_label="Team Member" name="Vipul Goyal" position="Lead, Processes and Personnel " image_url="http://www.electionpromisestracker.in/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/13094270_10154220485348436_4482630848393449287_n-1.jpg" animation="fade_in" background_layout="light" facebook_url="https://www.facebook.com/vipul.goyal" use_border_color="off" border_color="#ffffff" border_style="solid"]</p><p>A graduate from IIT Kanpur, Vipul spent his last 3 years teaching in a marginalized community in Delhi. Catch him in a cafe, with headphones on and a book in hand.</p><p>[/et_pb_team_member][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type="1_3"][et_pb_team_member admin_label="Team Member" name="Robin Keshaw" position="Lead, Partnerships &amp; Expansion" image_url="http://www.electionpromisestracker.in/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/12510264_10153752295005937_1406509919520404726_n-223x250-223x250.jpg" animation="fade_in" background_layout="light" use_border_color="off" border_color="#ffffff" border_style="solid" facebook_url="https://www.facebook.com/robin.keshaw"]</p><p>Robin Keshaw is Assignment Editor with NTI Media. He writes on development issues and policies. A computer science engineer from BITS, Pilani, he taught in a socially and economically marginalised community in Delhi as a Teach For India fellow. When he is not ''adulting'', you can find him teaching kids, writing poetry or trekking in mountains.</p><p>[/et_pb_team_member][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type="1_3"][et_pb_team_member admin_label="Team Member" name="Himanshu Gulati" position="Researcher" image_url="http://www.electionpromisestracker.in/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/10155462_642238059200590_2134138735067742745_n-250x250.jpg" animation="fade_in" background_layout="light" use_border_color="off" border_color="#ffffff" border_style="solid"]</p><p>Himanshu Gulati is an educator and helps kids enjoy Physics. Being agnostic, he could be found talking about religion, politics and theory. An observer, poet and finding the best ways to lead a fit life, he is also trying his hands at Photography these days.</p><p>[/et_pb_team_member][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row admin_label="row"][et_pb_column type="1_3"][et_pb_team_member admin_label="Team Member" name="Shubham Sarin" position="Lead, Technology" image_url="http://www.electionpromisestracker.in/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/13062350_1171502076216586_2696804551449870711_n-250x182.jpg" animation="fade_in" background_layout="light" use_border_color="off" border_color="#ffffff" border_style="solid"]</p><p>Shubham currently works as a Software Engineer at Paytm.</p><p>[/et_pb_team_member][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type="1_3"][et_pb_team_member admin_label="Team Member" name="Sajal Singh" position="Fact Checker" image_url="http://www.electionpromisestracker.in/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/18157323_10210986115722890_128516437352806744_n-165x190.jpg" animation="fade_in" background_layout="light" use_border_color="off" border_color="#ffffff" border_style="solid"]</p><p>Sajal is a politics enthusiast. A post graduate in Economics, he loves to debate and discuss politically incorrect issues and believes that nothing should be taboo in a mature democracy. He has been associated with a number of education start ups the most prominent being civilsdaily.</p><p>[/et_pb_team_member][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type="1_3"][et_pb_team_member admin_label="Team Member" name="Vidur Khanna" position="Technology" image_url="http://www.electionpromisestracker.in/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/13592756_1019941838102778_7998836317871435894_n-198x198.jpg" animation="fade_in" background_layout="light" use_border_color="off" border_color="#ffffff" border_style="solid"]</p><p>Vidur graduated from NIT Kurukshetra and currently works with PayTM.</p><p>[/et_pb_team_member][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row admin_label="row"][et_pb_column type="1_3"][et_pb_team_member admin_label="Team Member" name="Shriram" position="Intern" image_url="http://www.electionpromisestracker.in/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/11905774_932163730231454_9106338492012823653_n-250x160.jpg" animation="fade_in" background_layout="light" use_border_color="off" border_color="#ffffff" border_style="solid"]</p><p>Shriram is a graduate in Chemistry from St. Stephen''s College, Delhi.</p><p>[/et_pb_team_member][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type="1_3"][et_pb_team_member admin_label="Team Member" name="Munish Kaushik" position="Mentor" image_url="http://www.electionpromisestracker.in/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/pp-250x250.jpg" animation="fade_in" background_layout="light" use_border_color="off" border_color="#ffffff" border_style="solid"]</p><p>Munish is a development professional with a child-like heart. He has 16 years of experience of working for Child Rights and Disaster Management. He works with Delhi Government in education and participatory governance related projects. He has a really cool website. Do check out: http://www.munshiinpublicservice.com</p><p>[/et_pb_team_member][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type="1_3"][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section]</p>', 'About Us', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '789-autosave-v1', '', '', '2017-05-21 03:52:44', '2017-05-20 22:22:44', '', 789, 'http://www.electionpromisestracker.in/789-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
