(819, 3, '2017-05-27 17:43:39', '2017-05-27 12:13:39', '<span style="font-weight: 400;">India’s rank in </span><i><span style="font-weight: 400;">‘Ease of Doing Business</span></i><span style="font-weight: 400;">’ improved from </span><a href="http://www.thehindu.com/business/Economy/India-up-one-position-in-WB-ease-of-business-ranking/article16081515.ece"><span style="font-weight: 400;">142nd rank in 2014</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;"> to </span><a href="http://www.doingbusiness.org/rankings"><span style="font-weight: 400;">130th rank in 2016</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;">, according to World Bank.  This is an improvement of 12 places.  However, on the parameter of ‘</span><i><span style="font-weight: 400;">Starting A New Business</span></i><span style="font-weight: 400;">’, India’s rank slipped to </span><a href="http://www.doingbusiness.org/rankings"><span style="font-weight: 400;">155th rank in 2016</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;"> compared to </span><a href="http://www.business-standard.com/article/economy-policy/india-moves-up-by-just-one-notch-on-world-bank-s-ease-of-doing-business-index-116102501493_1.html"><span style="font-weight: 400;">151th rank in 2014</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;">.</span>\n\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">On the parameter of ‘</span><i><span style="font-weight: 400;">Getting Electricity</span></i><span style="font-weight: 400;">’ , India’s rank has been </span><a href="http://164.100.47.194/Loksabha/Questions/QResult15.aspx?qref=50242&amp;lsno=16"><span style="font-weight: 400;">improved </span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;">from 137th rank in 2015 to 26th rank in 2016. </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">The report has recognized the efforts of getting electricity in Delhi to make it faster and cheaper to obtain an electricity connection.</span>\n\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">The government </span><a href="http://economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/economy/policy/industrial-licence-validity-extended-to-three-years/articleshow/37676645.cms"><span style="font-weight: 400;">extended</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;"> the validity of industrial licence to 3 years and the industrial licence for defense to 15 years in July, 2014.</span>\n\nSince, India''s rank has been improved up to 12 places &amp; has space for the improvement in other parameters too, it has been', 'Will ensure that a conducive, enabling environment is created making ''doing business'' in India easy', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '432-autosave-v1', '', '', '2017-05-27 17:43:39', '2017-05-27 12:13:39', '', 432, 'http://www.electionpromisestracker.in/432-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
