IT Kanpur, Vipul spent his last 3 years teaching in a marginalized community in Delhi.\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_team_member][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type="1_3"][et_pb_team_member admin_label="Team Member" name="Robin Keshaw" position="Lead, Partnerships &amp; Expansion" image_url="http://www.electionpromisestracker.in/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/12510264_10153752295005937_1406509919520404726_n.jpg" animation="fade_in" background_layout="light" use_border_color="off" border_color="#ffffff" border_style="solid"]\r\n\r\nRobin Keshaw is Assignment Editor with NTI Media. He writes on development issues and policies. A computer science engineer from BITS, Pilani, he taught in an socially and economically community in Delhi as a Teach for India fellow. When he is not ''adulting'', you can find him teaching kids, writing poetry or trekking in mountains.\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_team_member][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type="1_3"][et_pb_team_member admin_label="Team Member" name="Himanshu Gulati" position="Researcher" image_url="http://www.electionpromisestracker.in/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/10155462_642238059200590_2134138735067742745_n.jpg" animation="fade_in" background_layout="light" use_border_color="off" border_color="#ffffff" border_style="solid"]\r\n\r\nHimanshu Gulati is an educator and helps kids enjoy Physics. Being agnostic, he could be find talking about religion, politics and theory. An observer, poet and finding the best ways to lead a fit life enthusiast, he is trying hands at Photography these days.\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_team_member][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row admin_label="row"][et_pb_column type="1_3"][et_pb_team_member admin_label="Team Member" name="Shubham Sarin" position="Lead, Technology" image_url="http://www.electionpromisestracker.in/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/13062350_1171502076216586_2696804551449870711_n.jpg" animation="fade_in" background_layout="light" use_border_color="off" border_color="#ffffff" border_style="solid"]\r\n\r\nShubham currently works as a Software Engineer at Paytm.\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_team_member][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type="1_3"][et_pb_team_member admin_label="Team Member" name="Sajal Singh" position="Fact Checker" image_url="http://www.electionpromisestracker.in/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/18157323_10210986115722890_128516437352806744_n.jpg" animation="fade_in" background_layout="light" use_border_color="off" border_color="#ffffff" border_style="solid"]\r\n\r\nSajal holds Masters in Economics from University of Delhi.\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_team_member][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type="1_3"][et_pb_team_member admin_label="Team Member" name="Vidur Khanna" position="Technology" image_url="http://www.electionpromisestracker.in/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/13592756_1019941838102778_7998836317871435894_n.jpg" animation="fade_in" background_layout="light" use_border_color="off" border_color="#ffffff" border_style="solid"]\r\n\r\nVidur graduated from NIT Kurukshetra and currently works with PayTM.\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_team_member][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row admin_label="row"][et_pb_column type="1_3"][et_pb_team_member admin_label="Team Member" name="Shriram" position="Intern" image_url="http://www.electionpromisestracker.in/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/11905774_932163730231454_9106338492012823653_n.jpg" animation="fade_in" background_layout="light" use_border_color="off" border_color="#ffffff" border_style="solid"]\r\n\r\nShriram is a graduate in Chemistry from St. Stephen''s College, Delhi.\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_team_member][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type="1_3"][et_pb_team_member admin_label="Team Member" name="Munish Kaushik" position="Intern" image_url="http://www.electionpromisestracker.in/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/pp.jpg" animation="fade_in" background_layout="light" use_border_color="off" border_color="#ffffff" border_style="solid"]\r\n\r\nMunish is an expert in disaster management,\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_team_member][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type="1_3"][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section]', 'About Us', '', '