 percent crop loss resulting from natural calamities, instead of earlier benchmark of 50 percent.', 'Implement a farm insurance scheme to take care of crop loss due to unforeseen natural calamities', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '558-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-06-01 23:22:39', '2017-06-01 17:52:39', '', 558, 'http://www.electionpromisestracker.in/558-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
